title: Ep. - 239 - THE BACHELOR AND REAL HOUSEWIVES REVIEWED BY PEOPLE WHO HAVE NEVER SEEN IT
description:
Kate asks the co-hosts of Lifetime After Hallmark podcast to review the christening episode of Real Housewives of New Jersey, and her sister Megan to watch her very first episode of The Bachelor. All the guests have never seen an episode of the show. 



Reality Life with Kate Casey
